  "page_title": "SML_ChangeAxisConfig (FB)",
  "text": "\nFUNCTION_BLOCK SML_ChangeAxisConfig\nModifies the axis configuration.\nThe gearing ratio, the movement type and the modulo period of the drive may be modified.\nAfter a change of the configuration, the axis is automatically restarted with\nSML_ReinitDrive\nin order to guarantee that all variables are initialized in a correct way.\nNote\nThe axis must be in state\nPowerOff\nto change the configuration.\n",
